{"type": "article", "id": 9227, "title": "单元式组合沙发", "description": "", "date": "2015-05-06T06:53:17Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 4, "image": "img/article/article_show/2016060523492815z2DX7RJNpMUxjy.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t设计师 Giulio Iacchetti 最近为 Casamania 推出了一套单元式组合沙发，沙发不同的模块之间由节点连接，既可以成为长沙发，又能变身两个半边扶手椅。其沙发坐垫上设有可拆卸的弹性亚麻布套，而沙发背面缝制了皮圈提手，方便更换沙发位置。这件产品在刚刚过去的米兰家具展上在第一次亮相。这是<a href=\"http://www.giulioiacchetti.com/\" target=\"_blank\">设计师的个人主页</a>，这是 <a href=\"http://www.casamania.it/\" target=\"_blank\">Casamania 的官方主页</a>，感兴趣的话，可以点击查看更多作品。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234925CoETujRxIQOJGLz7.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.6405868\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052349250giVlep3jPzoAQvO.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.62713936\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234926IFh2lAbVBTud5Cav.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.58190709\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234926iyFSnbjZ1C6mxqah.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052349262WD0dLbBgJypQMve.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.60513447\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234927X5Ympzl8ewOaJirE.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.83007335\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234927o2EIgfsv3SRHhyFe.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66136919\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}